From: Miklos Szeredi <miklos@szeredi.hu>
Subject: [FUSE] Add write file operation
Patch-mainline: 2.6.12-rc-mm

This patch adds the write filesystem operations of FUSE.

The following operations are added:

 o setattr
 o symlink
 o mknod
 o mkdir
 o create
 o unlink
 o rmdir
 o rename
 o link

